" <ESC> when typing 'jj' quick
inoremap jj <Esc>

" Select from the cursor to the end of line by typing 'vv' quick.
vnoremap v $

" Emacs like key-bindings in INSERT mode
imap <C-p> <Up>
imap <C-n> <Down>
imap <C-b> <Left>
imap <C-f> <Right>
imap <C-e> <End>
imap <C-a> <Home>
imap <C-h> <Backspace>
imap <C-d> <Del>
